Class FederationStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.query.algebra.evaluation.impl.StrictEvaluationStrategy

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluationStrategy, FederatedServiceResolver, FederatedServiceResolverClient, UUIDable

    public class FederationStrategy
extends StrictEvaluationStrategy
    Evaluates Join, LeftJoin and Union in parallel and only evaluate if OwnedTupleExpr is the given member.
    Author:
    James Leigh
    See Also:
    ParallelJoinCursor, ParallelLeftJoinCursor
